gười cha, Ego the Living Planet., nhưng cô ấy từ chối nói cho Quill biết sự thật, vì sợ khiến anh ấy nhớ lại những hành động khủng khiếp của cha mình. Sau khi động não tìm ý tưởng, họ đồng ý đến Trái đất và tìm lại người anh hùng thời thơ ấu của Quill, Kevin Bacon .</p>","tmdb_id":774752,"cast":["Chris Pratt","Dave Bautista","Karen Gillan","Pom Klementieff","Vin Diesel","Bradley Cooper","Sean Gunn","Rhett Miller","Murry Hammond","Ken Bethea","Philip Peeples","Michael Rooker","Kevin Bacon","Luke Klein","Maria Bakalova"],"director":["James Gunn"],"keywords":["holiday","superhero","celebrity","saving christmas","talking dog","based on movie","aftercreditsstinger","marvel cinematic universe (mcu)","christmas","christmas special","short film","holiday special","space dog"],"tmdb":{"type":"movie","id":"774752","season":null,"vote_average":7.095,"vote_count":2282},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Chris Pratt","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Chris Pratt","tmdb_id":73457,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cRH6HPAQ98PlOwwEvhYO4CM9lwu.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/73457"},{"name":"Dave Bautista","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Dave Bautista","tmdb_id":543530,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/snk6JiXOOoRjPtHU5VMoy6qbd32.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/543530"},{"name":"Karen Gillan","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Karen Gillan","tmdb_id":543261,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kFLXcFdok3ShDxylr3WNreQphQm.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/543261"},{"name":"Pom Klementieff","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Pom Klementieff","tmdb_id":139820,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hfUKAI2kXTMMWjno0i4sLPJud5N.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/139820"},{"name":"Vin Diesel","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Vin Diesel","tmdb_id":12835,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nZdVry7lnUkE24PnXakok9okvL4.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/12835"},{"name":"Bradley Cooper","name_vi"